{"sn9.14:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 9.14 ","sn9.14:0.2":"1. Vanavagga ","sn9.14:0.3":"Gandhatthenasutta ","sn9.14:1.1":"Ekam samayam annataro bhikkhu kosalesu viharati annatarasmim vanasande. ","sn9.14:1.2":"Tena kho pana samayena so bhikkhu pacchabhattam pindapatapatikkanto pokkharanim ogahetva padumam upasinghati. ","sn9.14:1.3":"Atha kho ya tasmim vanasande adhivattha devata tassa bhikkhuno anukampika atthakama tam bhikkhum samvejetukama yena so bhikkhu tenupasankami; upasankamitva tam bhikkhum gathaya ajjhabhasi: ","sn9.14:2.1":"“Yametam varijam puppham, ","sn9.14:2.2":"adinnam upasinghasi; ","sn9.14:2.3":"Ekangametam theyyanam, ","sn9.14:2.4":"gandhatthenosi marisa”ti. ","sn9.14:3.1":"“Na harami na bhanjami, ","sn9.14:3.2":"ara singhami varijam; ","sn9.14:3.3":"Atha kena nu vannena, ","sn9.14:3.4":"gandhatthenoti vuccati. ","sn9.14:4.1":"Yvayam bhisani khanati, ","sn9.14:4.2":"pundarikani bhanjati; ","sn9.14:4.3":"Evam akinnakammanto, ","sn9.14:4.4":"kasma eso na vuccati”ti. ","sn9.14:5.1":"“Akinnaluddo puriso, ","sn9.14:5.2":"dhaticelamva makkhito; ","sn9.14:5.3":"Tasmim me vacanam natthi, ","sn9.14:5.4":"tvancarahami vattave. ","sn9.14:6.1":"Ananganassa posassa, ","sn9.14:6.2":"niccam sucigavesino; ","sn9.14:6.3":"Valaggamattam papassa, ","sn9.14:6.4":"abbhamattamva khayati”ti. ","sn9.14:7.1":"“Addha mam yakkha janasi, ","sn9.14:7.2":"atho me anukampasi; ","sn9.14:7.3":"Punapi yakkha vajjasi, ","sn9.14:7.4":"yada passasi edisan”ti. ","sn9.14:8.1":"“Neva tam upajivama, ","sn9.14:8.2":"napi te bhatakamhase; ","sn9.14:8.3":"Tvameva bhikkhu janeyya, ","sn9.14:8.4":"yena gaccheyya suggatin”ti. ","sn9.14:9.1":"Atha kho so bhikkhu taya devataya samvejito samvegamapaditi. ","sn9.14:9.2":"Vanavaggo pathamo. ","sn9.14:10.0":"Tassuddanam ","sn9.14:10.1":"Vivekam upatthananca, ","sn9.14:10.2":"Kassapagottena sambahula; ","sn9.14:10.3":"Anando anuruddho ca, ","sn9.14:10.4":"Nagadattanca kulagharani. ","sn9.14:11.1":"Vajjiputto ca vesali, ","sn9.14:11.2":"Sajjhayena ayoniso; ","sn9.14:11.3":"Majjhanhikalamhi pakatindriya—","sn9.14:11.4":"Padumapupphena cuddasa bhaveti. ","sn9.14:11.5":"Vanasamyuttam samattam. "}